OL,3,CNumber of pensioners living in poverty
OL,4,Ccould double by 2040, charity warns
OL,6,FNew research by a charity that
OL,7,Fsupports older people facing hardship,
OL,8,Fshows the number of pensioners living
OL,9,Fbelow the poverty line in the UK could
OL,10,Fdouble in the next 15 years.
OL,12,FThis would mean that the figure would
OL,13,Fincrease from 2.1 million now to 3.9
OL,14,Fmillion people by 2040.
OL,16,FFurthermore, poverty levels among
OL,17,Folder people with a disability could
OL,18,Fincrease significantly from 18% to 29%.
