OL,3,CNumber of pensioners living in poverty
OL,4,Ccould double by 2040, charity warns
OL,6,FIndependent Age says these results
OL,7,Fpaint a bleak picture of what could
OL,8,Fhappen if political parties across the
OL,9,FUK take no action, and state it must
OL,10,Fbe a wake-up call ahead of the General
OL,11,FElection for all parties to act now to
OL,12,Fprevent widespread misery.
OL,14,FPoverty has been linked to a shortened
OL,15,Flife expectancy, a greater likelihood
OL,16,Fof poor physical and mental health,
OL,17,Fand increased stress and anxiety.
