OL,3,CNumber of pensioners living in poverty
OL,4,Ccould double by 2040, charity warns
OL,6,FIndependent Age says there are too
OL,7,Fmany people like Yvonne who are over
OL,8,F65 and living below the poverty line.
OL,10,FChief Executive, Joanna Elson CBE,
OL,11,Fbelieves this is a scandal.
OL,13,FShe says the older people the charity
OL,14,Fspeaks to are already in financial
OL,15,Fhardship and skipping meals, washing
OL,16,Fin cold water or not using the lights
OL,17,Fin the evening, all to save money.
